<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Forgot Password - Taco Joes Rewards</title>
    <link href="style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <img src="tacoJoesImage.jpg">

        <h1 class="orange">Recover Your Account</h1>

        <p>You recently requested to reset your Taco Joes Rewards password. Use the temporary password provided below to log in to your account.</p>
            
        <p>Once logged in, please change your password. This temporary password will no longer be available after logging in.</p>
        
        <p class="bold">Temporary Password:</p>
        <div class="password-container">
            <h1><%= mailOptionsAdditions.password %></h1>
        </div>
        
    </div>
    
    
</body>
</html>